# Gymnasium Project Plan

## Objectives
Develop a user-friendly web application for tracking gym exercises. The application will analyze the collected data to identify trends and provide personalized recommendations.

## Planning
- **Phase 1**: Definition of MVP and its requirements (1 week)
- **Phase 2**: Design and prototyping (3 weeks)
- **Phase 3**: Development (6 weeks)
- **Phase 4**: Testing (1 weeks)
- **Phase 5**: Deployment (1 week)

## Backlog
1. User authentication
2. Task creation and management
3. Notifications
4. Reporting and analytics

## Wish List
- **User Authentication**: Secure login and registration.
- **Task Management**: Create, update, delete, and view tasks.
- **Notifications**: Generic.
- **Reporting**: Generate reports on task completion and productivity.
- Que al colocar mi celular en un soporte de la maquina registre la informacion de mi ejercicio.- Esto puede darse por NFC.
- Que sea facil para mi ingresar la informacion del ejercicio que acabo de hacer.
- Que al entrar al gimnasio no me olvide de iniciar la app el registro de actividades. Que me detecte la locacion o la actividad y me sugiera empezar a registrar ejercicio
- Que me muestra la info del ultimo peso y cuantas series hice en esa maquina
- Que me muestre un historico del peso y series a lo largo del tiempo
- It should have all images and information about each machine or equipment.
- All machines/equipment are associated with refence numbers of SmartFit.
- Each time I enter a record, it has to go to a historic.
- I have to be able to get plots and data from the historic about my progress.
- I must be able to enter my working weight, set, reps for each machine/equipment.
- It should be simple to enter a record and find it.
- Asociar los ejercicios por dia
- Poder ingresar una fecha especifica y el ejercicio
- Hacer la interfaz con Js, html, Css
- Utilizar MySQL.